{"title":"远征","authors":["宫玺"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":10,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"远征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫玺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛长鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮飞滚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车载我们出发了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走上遥远的征程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们这一群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽说来自四面八方，面孔陌生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是奋斗的目标相同，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为共产主义事业而斗争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的乳汁哺养我们长大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想滋润着我们的心灵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要做红色接班人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把革命大旗高擎更高擎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们出发了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江黄河为我们壮行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们豪迈的、火热的歌呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压息了大西北漠漠的砂尘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要为祖国开发粮仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在荒漠的土地上播种歌声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让汗珠变成米粒和棉桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让砂石变成美丽的新城！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们向往那美好的未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们热爱战斗的人生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让理想在边疆开花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让祖国更繁荣，更强盛！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}